I have completed the redesign of the Invoicer UI and created the three requested files:

1.  **`design-brief.md`**: Contains the shared design system for the prototypes, detailing the color tokens (Indigo/Slate), typography scale, spacing system, component variants, and responsive strategies.
2.  **`landing-prototype.html`**: A complete marketing website mockup using plain HTML/CSS (via Tailwind CSS CDN) with sections for Hero, Features, and Pricing, focusing on a "free forever" message with premium styling.
3.  **`app-prototype.html`**: A comprehensive in-app UI mockup that covers all the required screens from the `functional-spec.md` (Login, Register, Forgot Password, Onboarding, Dashboard, Invoices List, Invoice Create/Edit, Invoice Detail, Clients List, Catalog, and Settings). It uses a lightweight JavaScript router to toggle between the different screens, ensuring they all feel like one cohesive product family.
